 Core Pages
Landing Page — Introduction to Karuteens, registration, and overview of main features.
Home / News Feed — Aggregated posts from friends, groups, and pages.
Profile (Timeline) — User’s personal posts, bio, photos, and friends list.
Search — Discover people, pages, posts, groups, events, and marketplace listings.
Notifications — All alerts about interactions, messages, and system updates.
Settings & Privacy — Manage account, security, visibility, and preferences.

 Social & Communication
Messenger — 1:1 and group chats, calls, voice messages, and media sharing.
Reels / Stories — Short videos and time-limited stories with music and stickers.
Watch / Video — Long-form videos, series, and content subscriptions.
Memories — View and reshare past posts or milestones.

 Community & Collaboration
Groups — Join or create communities for classes, topics, or clubs.
Study Rooms — Virtual rooms with shared whiteboards and collaboration tools.
Pages — Public or business profiles for creators, organizations, and brands.
Creator Studio — Manage posts, insights, and monetization as a creator.
Events — Discover or create online/offline events, RSVP, and ticket management.
Campus Life Hub — Campus map, activities, club events, and room booking.
AI Study Buddy — Personalized academic assistant powered by AI.
Exam Resources — Past papers, notes, and unit-based study materials.

 Marketplace & Commerce
Marketplace — Buy/sell items, services, and listings.
Product Detail Page — View product info, images, and contact seller.
Seller Dashboard — Manage listings, sales, and shop analytics.
Cart / Checkout — Review and complete purchases.
Payment Page — M-Pesa and crypto payment integrations.

 Events & Entertainment
Event Listing Page — Browse all upcoming and trending events.
Event Detail Page — View event info, RSVP, and join online sessions.
Entertainment Arena — Watch movies, shows, and student content streams.
Fundraisers / Donations — Contribute to verified student or community causes.

 Education & Study Tools
Study Dashboard — Overview of study progress, achievements, and AI suggestions.
Peer Tutoring Marketplace — Find or offer tutoring services.
Study Calendar — Schedule sessions, reminders, and upcoming exams.
Collaboration Notes — Shared document editing and uploads.
Leaderboards — Track academic progress and achievements.

 Finance & Monetization
Payments & Wallet — Manage transactions, subscriptions, and micro-payments.
Ads Manager — Create and monitor promotional campaigns.
Revenue Dashboard — Track income from subscriptions, sales, or ads.
Premium Features — Unlock advanced AI tools or study features.

 Safety, Help & Admin
Help & Support — FAQs, ticket submission, and support chat.
Report Center — Report users, content, or issues.
Safety Center — Mental health, campus security, and emergency contacts.
Admin Dashboard — Moderation, analytics, and system management.
Verification Portal — Verify student identity via university email.

 PWA & System Features
Offline Mode Page — View cached content when offline.
Push Notifications Page — Manage notification preferences.
Language & Region Settings — Choose language and country content.
Legal Pages — Terms of Service, Privacy Policy, Cookie Consent.

